### ============================================================
### 길드 관리 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 생성
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Runners",
  "description": "A guild for people who love morning runs",
  "category": "HEALTH",
  "isPublic": true,
  "maxMembers": 50
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 상세 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 공개 길드 목록 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/public?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 검색
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/search?keyword=runners&page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 길드 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/my
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 정보 수정
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Runners Club",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "maxMembers": 100
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 마스터 권한 이양
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/transfer-master
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "newMasterId": "new-master-user-id"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 멤버 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/members
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 탈퇴
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/members/me
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 가입 신청 (공개 길드)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/join-requests
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "message": "I'd love to join your guild!"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 가입 신청 목록 (마스터 전용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/join-requests?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 가입 신청 승인 (마스터 전용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/join-requests/1/approve
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 가입 신청 거절 (마스터 전용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/join-requests/1/reject
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "reason": "Sorry, we're not accepting new members at this time"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 멤버 초대 (비공개 길드, 마스터 전용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/members/invitee-user-id
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드 경험치/레벨 정보 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/experience
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### 길드 채팅 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 전송
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Nickname: {{userNickname}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 최신 메시지 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat?page=0&size=50
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 새 메시지 조회 (폴링)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/new?since=2025-01-15T10:00:00
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 ID 이후 메시지 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/after/100
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 이전 메시지 조회 (무한 스크롤)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/before/100?page=0&size=50
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 검색
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/search?keyword=hello&page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
